regents consisting of the Vice-President, the Chief
Justice, three members of the United States Sen-
ate, three members of the House of Representa-
tives, and six citizens of the United States appointed
by joint resolution of Congress. The secretary of
the Smithsonian Institution is its executive officer
and the director of its activities.

