As to the contention that the President and Steel
Corporation prevented “a general industrial ‘smash-
up,’ ” it is stoutly maintained by Colonel Roosevelt
and by Judge Gary that -the advantage in the
“sweetening” of Grant B. Schley’s ob1igations——that
