THE MINIMUM WAGE.

Within the last four years eleven States have en-
acted minimum wage laws. Massachusetts was the
ﬁrst (in 1912), though its act did not go into effect
until after ﬁve other acts were in operation. The
dates at which the laws became effective (1913 ex-
cept Arkansas and Kansas, 1915) .were as follows:_

 

Utah. . . . . . . . . . . . . .May 13 Nebraska. . . . . . . . ..July 17
